"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/759339","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","false","2017-09-19","<p>The transfer of the islands of Tiran and Sanafir is a sovereign matter between Egypt and Saudi Arabia. The UK Government has not had any substantive discussions on the matter with the Egyptian Government.</p>","North East Bedfordshire","Alistair Burt",,"2017-09-19T10:38:18.033Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/759339/answer","Biography information for Alistair Burt","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/759339/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/759339/answer",,,,,"16","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","2017-09-11","Egypt: Saudi Arabia","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Foreign and Commonwealth Affairs, what discussions his Department has had with the Egyptian Government on the transfer of Tiran and Sanafir Islands to Saudi Arabia.","false","Biography information for Jim Shannon","Strangford","Jim Shannon","10009"
